name: Ariel:Sprite Bound2Serve
description:
Magic Sprite rescu'd from a tree, his fate now bound to s'rve thee. 
Ariel imprison by a mistress's spell, is anon the s'rvant who s'rves thee well.
All eyes and ears and all mann'r of f'rest beasts, he s'rves the usurp'd ex-duke & his daught'r, miranda at deprivation or feast. 
Tempest's Sprite shall foil or turneth thee and thee, Lioness Sprite stayeth in comf'rt to me.
29.9MP, 4096x7296, 28MB
